                     <interp inst="t18431127-235-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 breast-pin, value 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 handkerchief, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 sixpence; the property of <persName id="t18431127-name-1272" type="victimName">
